Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}Lead the way
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}Take me home
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}Take me home
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}思い出は明日の道しるべ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}回憶是引領明日的路標
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}ほら　ほら　帰ろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}走吧 走吧 我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}With you　僕らの街へ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}帶你一起去我們的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}見上げた星は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}頭上的漫天星星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}過去のかがやき
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}都是曾經的輝煌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:15:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}優しくて寂しい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:15:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}溫柔且孤單
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}だけど大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}但是不用害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}息をするたび
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}每當我呼吸之時
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}感じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}我都能感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}僕の中の「君」を
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}我心中的「你」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}知らない未来も
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}即使是未知的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}きっと怖くない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}也無需畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}Lead the way
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}Lead the way
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}Take me home
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}Take me home
